                     <interp inst="t17781209-27-verdict170" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder1s"></interp>
               GUILTY of stealing to the value of 10 d.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Tried by the First Middlesex Jury before Mr. Baron HOTHAM.</p>
